DEPRESSION & RELATED MOOD DISORDERS

Intense Ongoing Sadness accompanied with Loss of Interest, Guilt, Low Self Esteem, Sense of Helplessness, Change in Appetite, Sleep Disturbance & Suicidal Thoughts That Lasts for Several Weeks May Be Indicative Of
 Clinical Depression or Major Depression,
A Serious Disabling & Possibly Life Threatening Psychiatric Condition
That Requires Urgent Medical Attention

TREATMENT APPROACH 

Our Team of Doctors, Nurses and Counselors are
Experienced in the Multimodal Treatment of Depression 

Cognitive Behavior Therapy, Family & InterPersonal Therapies,
Life Style Coaching, as Well as Antidepressants,
Natural Remedies & Supplements
are Recommended to Alleviate Symptoms
